@startuml

title Marketplace Seller Review and User Report Submission Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant "Frontend (Website)" as FE
participant "Apache\n(HTTP Server)" as Apache

box "Laravel Application" #LightGreen
  participant "Middleware" as MW
  participant "ReviewController" as RC
  participant "UserReportController" as URC
  participant "Eloquent ORM" as ORM
end box

database "MariaDB Database" as DB

note right of User
It is assumed the User is
authenticated/authorized unless an exception occurs.
end note


== Submit Seller Rating ==

User -> FE: Select seller rating and click "Enviar Calificación"
activate User
activate FE
activate Apache
activate MW
activate RC
activate URC
activate ORM
activate DB

FE -> Apache: POST /marketplace/{post}/review

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP seller review request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display "Seller review route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> RC: Pass authenticated and authorized seller review request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden / 422 Unprocessable Entity
    FE --> User: Display validation or authorization error
end

RC -> ORM: Resolve target post and seller
ORM -> DB: SELECT post and seller data needed for review submission

alt Post and seller found
    DB --> ORM: Post and seller record
    ORM --> RC: Review target retrieved
else Post or seller not found
    DB --> ORM: Empty result set
    ORM --> RC: Review target not found
    RC --> FE: 404 Not Found / 422 Unprocessable Entity
    FE --> User: Display selected seller not available for review
end

RC -> ORM: Create or update seller review
ORM -> DB: INSERT INTO reviews (...) OR UPDATE existing review

alt Review persistence success
    DB --> ORM: Insert/update successful
    ORM --> RC: Seller review persisted

    RC -> ORM: Recalculate seller rating average and review count
    ORM -> DB: SELECT AVG(rating), COUNT(*) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

    alt Aggregate refresh success
        DB --> ORM: Updated seller rating metrics
        ORM --> RC: Seller rating aggregates retrieved
        RC --> FE: Return success response with updated rating metrics
        FE --> User: Show rating success confirmation
    else Aggregate refresh failure
        DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
        ORM --> RC: Seller rating aggregate retrieval failed
        RC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
        FE --> User: Display system error while refreshing seller rating
    end

else Review persistence failure
    DB --> ORM: Insert/update failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> RC: Seller review persistence failed
    RC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> User: Display system error while submitting seller rating
end


== Submit User Report ==

User -> FE: Select report reason, write description, and click "Enviar Querella"
FE -> Apache: POST /reports

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP user report request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display "User report route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> URC: Pass authenticated and authorized report request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden / 422 Unprocessable Entity
    FE --> User: Display validation or authorization error
end

URC -> ORM: Resolve reported user and report target context
ORM -> DB: SELECT reported user and related reporting context

alt Report target found
    DB --> ORM: Report target record
    ORM --> URC: Report target retrieved
else Report target not found
    DB --> ORM: Empty result set
    ORM --> URC: Report target not found
    URC --> FE: 404 Not Found / 422 Unprocessable Entity
    FE --> User: Display selected user not available for reporting
end

URC -> ORM: Create marketplace user report with reason and description
ORM -> DB: INSERT INTO reports (...)

alt Report persistence success
    DB --> ORM: Insert successful
    ORM --> URC: Marketplace report persisted
    URC --> FE: Return success response
    FE --> User: Show report submission confirmation
else Report persistence failure
    DB --> ORM: Insert failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> URC: Marketplace report persistence failed
    URC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> User: Display system error while submitting report
end

@enduml